    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Older poor-condition vehicle being sold honestly as-is. It shows clear cosmetic wear inside and out, with noticeable age, use, and likely deferred maintenance, so buyers should expect a project rather than a turn-key car. Best suited for someone handy, a fixer-upper candidate, or possibly parts, but it could also appeal to a very budget-minded buyer who understands what it is. Please come with realistic expectations and inspect thoroughly.",
