    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Value-priced and sold as-is, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation for the right buyer. Best suited for someone seeking a budget commuter, project car, or handy second vehicle, it presents a practical opportunity at an accessible price. If you want straightforward value and understand the appeal of a lower-cost vehicle with potential, this one is worth a look.",
