    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A car with real presence and a story in every mile, this one has the kind of honest, lived-in character that turns heads for all the right reasons. It\u2019s an ideal find for someone who appreciates grit, style, and the chance to make a vehicle truly their own\u2014whether you need a budget-friendly daily, a practical project, or simply something with personality that stands apart from the ordinary. Affordable, distinctive, and full of potential, this is the kind of ride that rewards the right owner.",
      "price": 6900.0,
